# Claude Code: keep the directory local by default — sub-agents spawned with
# `isolation: "worktree"` create transient working copies under
# .claude/worktrees/, and personal overrides live in settings.local.json.
# But the *shared* hook config (the Biome Stop-gate) must be checked in so it
# applies to every agent/session, so re-include those specific paths.
.claude/*
!.claude/settings.json
!.claude/hooks/
!.claude/skills/
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/worktrees/
